text\": \"Carew\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rod_Carew\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rod_Carew\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ms Bass said at the airport that she felt a \\\"tremendous pride and responsibility\\\" in being given the Olympic Flag in Paris.\", \"from\": 562, \"to\": 685, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 565, \"end\": 569, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bass_guitar\", \"score\": 0.9999976203856595, \"rank\": 2.373665502984969e-06, \"text\": \"Bass\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bass_guitar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bass_guitar\"}, {\"begin\": 679, \"end\": 684, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999998258545, \"rank\": 1.7413865207448632e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While Los Angeles has been putting in the work to host a great Games, the mayor said American organisers now really felt the \\\"need to put our foot on the gas\\\".\", \"from\": 687, \"to\": 846, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 693, \"end\": 704, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999923287738075, \"rank\": 7.671263935981916e-06, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}, {\"begin\": 772, \"end\": 780, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Airlines\", \"score\": 0.7181919884288577, \"rank\": 0.3923851075661257, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q46970\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Airlines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Airlines\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The International Olympic Committee awarded Los Angeles the right in 2017 to host the 2028 Games.\", \"from\": 848, \"to\": 945, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 852, \"end\": 883, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 892, \"end\": 903, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999923287738075, \"rank\": 7.671263935981916e-06, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It will be the third time LA has hosted the Games in the modern era, after being the host city in 1932 and 1984.\", \"from\": 946, \"to\": 1058, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ms Bass acknowledged Paris had set a high bar as an Olympic host, and that LA's homelessness problem would be a challenge to overcome.\", \"from\": 1060, \"to\": 1194, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1063, \"end\": 1067, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bass_guitar\", \"score\": 0.9999976203856595, \"rank\": 2.373665502984969e-06, \"text\": \"Bass\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bass_guitar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bass_guitar\"}, {\"begin\": 1081, \"end\": 1086, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999998258545, \"rank\": 1.7413865207448632e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympic officials in Paris handed the flag to their American counterparts during the closing ceremony.\", \"from\": 1196, \"to\": 1298, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1217, \"end\": 1222, \"title\": \"http:/